title: High school roundup: Vestal outduels M-E
text:
High school roundup: Vestal outduels M-E 
By wbng sports October 9, 2015 Updated Oct 9, 2015 at 12:34 AM EDT 
Vestal, NY (WBNG Binghamton) Vestal won a back-and-forth second set, 29-27, over Maine-Endwell in girl's volleyball on Thursday night. That helped propel the Golden Bears to a win over the Spartans in four sets. 
It was some redemption of sorts for Vestal because M-E won the first meeting between the two teams earlier this year.
